Author: WILSON
Vol / Page: 43
Edition:
Quote: CUCUMBER FISH A small marine fish which is related to the lizard-fish and the lantern-fish and gets its name because it smells like sliced, fresh cucumber. ... Often confused with the [smelt] (they both smell of cucumber) but no relation.
